PATTERN CAUSED

pattern_caused recognizes "caused" used where "cause" or "course" was intended
the trailing -ed ending is sometimes typed when only the bare verb was meant

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_caused:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan for "caused" in contexts incompatible with its past-tense meaning

VERB correct
substitute the intended word silently based on surrounding context
